{"tid":2059469,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國全球宗教自由報告 狠批中國壓迫宗教 國務卿蓬佩奧：我們有法治，中國沒有","createTime":"2020-06-11T02:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T05:00:54.000Z","uid":70063,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"758ad73f306985ee599c9f7806111d2584fb9938","tid":2059469,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T02:51:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1270871096527597568?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1270871096527597568%3Fs%3D19&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRM1lVRHyxjHm7NpFearlrcU%3D&h=498fb6cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecPompeo%2Fstatus%2F1270871096527597568%3Fs%3D19&h=46197a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SecPompeo/status/1270871096527597568?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發布《全球宗教自由年度報告》，國務卿蓬佩奧在記者會上表示，過去一年，中國的宗教自由狀況進一步轉差，中共新疆對維吾爾人、藏傳佛教、法輪功以至基督教的壓制持續。他又再批中國官員以黑人男子弗洛伊德（George Floyd）死亡引發騷亂事件造文章，指美中在保障人權上差太遠，不能相提並論。<br />\n<br />\n報告花了 4.5 萬字篇幅寫中國情況，指過去一年，中共政府對宗教人士，不論是已登記或未登記的宗教團體，施以虐待、暴力、拘捕、囚禁，以及強迫灌輸中共教條。持續大規模拘留新疆維吾爾人，又鎮壓佛教徒、藏人、法輪功和基督徒。報告特別提到成都秋雨聖約教會王怡牧師被指煽動顛覆國家政權罪和非法經營罪判囚&nbsp;9 年。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧在記者會上再次批評北京以美國黑人男子弗洛伊德（George Floyd）被警員壓頸致死事件做文章，指美國自身種族歧視嚴重，卻對其他國家人權狀況說三道四。蓬佩奧說，美中兩國不能相提並論：「我們有法治，中國沒有；我們有言論自由，擁抱和平示威，中國不會。我們保障宗教自由&hellip;&hellip;中國則多年來持續打壓宗教信仰。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A3%93%E8%BF%AB%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99-%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%9C%89%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E7%258B%25A0%25E6%2589%25B9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A3%2593%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2595%2599-%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%2F&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRM1lVRHyxjHm7NpFearlrcU%3D&h=28e4349f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E7%258B%25A0%25E6%2589%25B9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A3%2593%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2595%2599-%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%2F&h=925b839c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A3%93%E8%BF%AB%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99-%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E6%9C%89%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89/</a>"},{"pid":"3bc2a4f8ac2915fc44becfec7e96c1d2e973b37f","tid":2059469,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T02:53:44.000Z","msg":"所有人權牌都一次過拎哂出黎打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終極目標係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36df11878c6929bbd06b9e880293238174fd3ea1","tid":2059469,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class